[http://download.modem-help.co.uk/mfcs-S/Sitecom/WL-106-54M-Wireless-Broadband-Home-Station/ Downloads on m-h] Firmware strings indicate this device was manufactured or designed by '''SerComm''' (model IP816T ??), uses a '''Brecis''' SoC, and uses a '''Intersil''' p54 based wireless module. This device probably uses a '''ADMtek''' ADM6996 Switch.. and perhaps a '''NEC''' USB 2.0 controller. The default SSID may be '''Sitecom''' or '''default'''.
